12.info_text:
Welcome to Galactica V!

You are the first to arrive on this planet. It's a blank slate waiting for you to make your mark.
You can build up to 7 buildings on this planet.
There are no special buildings available on this planet.
Possible resources on this planet include:

- population
- water
- technology
- energy
- minerals
- food

The planet's orbits around its sun at a distance of 2.5M km with a speed of 2.7km/s.
